net.sandius.rembulan

Class PlainValueTypeNamer

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sandius.rembulan.PlainValueTypeNamer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ValueTypeNamer

    public class PlainValueTypeNamer
extends Object
implements ValueTypeNamer
    A value type namer that uses a fixed mapping from types to type names.

    This is a wrapper of the static method luaTypeToName(LuaType).

      • luaTypeToName

        public static String luaTypeToName(LuaType type)
        Returns the name (a string) of a given Lua type.

        The result of this method is one of "nil", "boolean", "number", "string", "table", "function", "userdata" and "thread".

        Parameters:
        type - the type, must not be null
        Returns:
        the name of type
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if type is null
